Introduction

Jei is a South Korean singer, actress, and YouTuber currently under Mars Entertainment and Bomnal Entertainment. She is a member and the Leader, Vocalist, and Visual of the South Korean girl group FIESTAR under FAVE Entertainment.

She offically debuted as a member in FIESTAR on August 31, 2012 with the single album "Vista", with the title track of the same name.
